    "description": "欢迎来到一个速度与策略融合的世界，展开难忘的比赛！骑上你的巨鸟，穿越充满意外障碍和超车机会的环形赛道。超越对手，利用战术和各种工具冲到前面。你准备好迎接挑战，成为这些极限比赛的传奇了吗？ <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/24934cdf356c8677321287df580857bd.webp?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=25 /></span> <br><strong>在巨鸟上超越对手，参与动态比赛</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/08d4f15d3a59b1f81595516b6b57f658.poster.avif?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/08d4f15d3a59b1f81595516b6b57f658.webm?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/08d4f15d3a59b1f81595516b6b57f658.mp4?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>沉浸在极速竞赛的世界中！在各种地点的独特赛道上竞速，躲避障碍物，精准射击目标以赚取额外积分。单人游戏中感受肾上腺素的冲击，或在精彩的多人游戏中与朋友一决高下。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/24934cdf356c8677321287df580857bd.webp?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=25 /></span> <br><strong>用尽一切手段赢得胜利</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/812ed2c6dc2f5731e179a028467cd147.poster.avif?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/812ed2c6dc2f5731e179a028467cd147.webm?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/812ed2c6dc2f5731e179a028467cd147.mp4?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>为了争夺第一名，没有规则可言！用枪射击、用棍子打击、使用鞭子，或者扔绳子和石头来减缓你的对手。展现你的战术技巧和机智，超越所有人，率先冲过终点线。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/24934cdf356c8677321287df580857bd.webp?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=25 /></span> <br><strong>通过定制表达你的独特风格</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/0b62289f1732339c4d235d648853adcd.poster.avif?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/0b62289f1732339c4d235d648853adcd.webm?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/0b62289f1732339c4d235d648853adcd.mp4?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>利用广泛的定制选项，让你的角色脱颖而出。为你和你的鸟选择各种独特的服装和配饰，在赛道上突出个性，展示你的独特风格。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/24934cdf356c8677321287df580857bd.webp?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=25 /></span>",
